rovided.","Heading.OSA.illegalContentReportAppealNewEmail":"Illegal Content Report Appeal - Automated Reply","Message.ConnectionRequestAcceptedDouble":"{userOne} and {userTwo} accepted your Connection request.","Message.ConnectionRequestAcceptedMultiple":"{userOne}, {userTwo}, and {userMultipleCount, plural, =1 {# other} other {# others}} accepted your Connection request.","Message.ConnectionRequestAcceptedSingle":"{userOne} accepted your Connection request.","Message.ConnectionRequestSentDouble":"{userOne} and {userTwo} sent you Connection requests.","Message.ConnectionRequestSentFromContacts":"{userOne} sent you a Connection request from their phone contacts.","Message.ConnectionRequestSentMultiple":"{userOne}, {userTwo}, and {userMultipleCount, plural, =1 {# other} other {# others}} sent you Connection requests.","Message.ConnectionRequestSentSingle":"{userOne} sent you a Connection request.","Message.TooManyConnectionsOther":"That user already has the max number of Connections.","Message.TooManyConnectionsSelf":"You already have the max number of Connections.","Message.YouHaveNewConnectionRequests":"You have {numberOfRequests} new {numberOfRequests, plural, =1 {Connection request} other {Connections requests}}.","Message.YouHaveNewConnections":"You have {numberOfFriends} new {numberOfFriends, plural, =1 {Connection} other {Connections}}.","Message.ConnectionConfirmedDouble":"{userOne} and {userTwo} are now your Connections!","Message.ConnectionConfirmedMultiple":"{userOne}, {userTwo}, and {userMultipleCount, plural, =1 {# other} other {# others}} are now your Connections!","Message.ConnectionConfirmedSingle":"{userOne} is now your Connection!","AbuseReason.RewardedAdsPublisherViolation":"Your experience showed Rewarded Ads that violated one of the following: showing ad(s) that users did not ask for, providing misleading reward(s), or not providing reward(s).","Heading.RewardedAdExperienceRejected":"Rewarded Ad Publishing Violation","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Sharing support resources if you need them: Your well-being is our priority, and we want to make sure you have access to support if you need it. You reported content that may be harmful to children and that may have been upsetting. If you are in a moment where talking to someone could help, we offer access to helplines: https://roblox.findahelpline.com/. While these resources may be a starting point, we encourage you to reach out to someone you trust to discuss how you are feeling. \n\nThank you for submitting a content harmful to children report under the UK Online Safety Act. We have received your submission and it is pending review. Our estimated timeframe for deciding content harmful to children reports is within 3 business days. Please note this is only indicative, as it depends on many factors, including the complexity of the issues raised and how much relevant information you have included in your report. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nContent URL: {contentURL}\n\nFollowing our review of your complaint, we may decide that the content you reported violates Roblox’s Community Standards (if so, we will remove the content) or we may decide that the content you reported does not violate Roblox’s Community Standards (if so, we will not remove the content). \n\nYou will receive an update with our decision and details on any action taken to the contact email you provided.\nIf you would like to submit an additional report, please visit our reporting page: https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportNoViolation":"No Violation (OSA Reported Content Not Removed)","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportNoViolation":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act  - content harmful to children report.\nAfter review of your submitted report, we have concluded that the content does not violate Roblox's Community Standards. As a result, we will not take action on the content you reported.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportContentRemoved":"Violation (OSA Reported Content Removed)","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportContentRemoved":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report.\nAfter review of your submitted report, we have concluded that the content violates Roblox's Community Standards and has been removed:\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nContent URL: {contentURL}\n\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportUserModerated":"Violation (OSA Reported User Removed)","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportUserModerated":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report.\nAfter review of your submitted report, we have concluded that the behavior violates Roblox's Community Standards and the user has been moderated at the time of this response:\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportGeneralInquiries":"Report Irrelevant for CHCR - General Inquiries","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportGeneralInquiries":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report.\nWe are sorry, but we are unable to provide you assistance through this reporting channel. For general inquiries, please visit our Support form. If you would like to report content that violates Roblox’s Community Standards, learn more about reporting a rule violation. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportLawEnforcement":"Report From Law Enforcement","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportLawEnforcement":"Thank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report. In order to be able to process this request efficiently, we kindly request that you submit it through our Law Enforcement Portal which can be found here: https://app.kodexglobal.com/roblox/signin. \nYou can find more information in our FAQs for law enforcement here: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/11219680442260-Help-Center-FAQs-for-Law-Enforcement.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportInsufficientInformation":"Insufficient Information for Content Harmful to Children Review","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportInsufficientInformation":"Hello,\n\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report.\nAfter review of your report, we have determined that there is insufficient information in your report to determine whether what has been reported is harmful to children.\n\nPlease note that the \"report abuse\" functionality enables users to report violative chat directly.\n\nIf you would like to submit a new report with additional details, please visit:   https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting. \nIf you believe your account was hacked, please get in touch with Roblox’s Customer Support: https://www.roblox.com/support.\n\nLearn more about your further rights for redress here: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000245263-Appeal-Your-Content-or-Account-Moderation. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\n\nSincerely,\n\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportNewReport":"Please Submit a New Report","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportNewReport":"We are sorry, but we are unable to provide you with any further information or response regarding this inquiry. We encourage you to review the previous information sent to you, as we have provided you with all that we can at this time. If you would like to submit an additional report, please visit our reporting page: https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting.\nHowever, if you need further assistance with a different matter, please visit our Support Form: https://www.roblox.com/support.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportContentAlreadyRemoved":"Content Already Removed","Description.CHCR.illegalContentReportContentAlreadyRemoved":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Online Safety Act - content harmful to children report.\nWe are unable to review your report because the content you reported is no longer available on our services. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.CHCR.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Content Harmful to Children Report - Automated Reply to Newly Created Tickets","DisableMiddleEastChat.Title":"Chat is restricted in your region","DisableMiddleEastChat.Body":"Chat features are currently unavailable in your region.","Description.AdRejected":"Our moderation has removed your Ad ID: {ContentID}","Heading.AdRejected":"Ad Removed","Heading.AdAppealUpdated":"Your appeal on ad (ID: {ContentID}) is updated.","Description.AdAppealUpdated":"Appeal request: Ad ID: {ContentID}","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNoViolation":"No Violation (OSA Reported Content Not Removed)","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportInsufficientInfo":"Hello,\n\nThank you for submitting an Australian Online Safety Act Content Report.\nAfter review of your report, we have determined that there is insufficient information in your report to determine whether what has been reported violates Roblox’s Community Standards or is regulated under cited Australian laws.\n\nPlease note that the \"report abuse\" functionality enables users to report violative chat directly.\n\nIf you would like to submit a new report with additional details, please visit:   https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting. \nIf you believe your account was hacked, please get in touch with Roblox’s Customer Support: https://www.roblox.com/support.\nLearn more about your further rights for redress here: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000245263-Appeal-Your-Content-or-Account-Moderation. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\n\nSincerely,\n\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNoViolation":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Australian Online Safety Act Content report.\nAfter review of your submitted report, we have concluded that the content does not violate Roblox's Community Standards or require us to take action under cited local laws. As a result, we will not take action on the content you reported.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\nIf you would like to appeal our decision,  please use the following case ID and link:\nCase ID: {caseID}\nAppeal Link: {appealLink}\n\nLearn more about your rights to appeal our decision: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/360000245263-Appeal-Your-Content-or-Account-Moderation.\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportGeneralInquiries":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Australian Online Safety Act Content Report.\nWe are sorry, but we are unable to provide you assistance through this reporting channel because the report is not in relation to content regulated under the Australian Online Safety Act. For general inquiries, please visit our Support form: https://www.roblox.com/support. If you would like to report content that violates Roblox’s Community Standards, learn more about reporting a rule violation: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/203312410-How-to-Report-Rule-Violations. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Illegal Content Report - Automated Reply to Newly Created Tickets","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Thank you for submitting a harmful, illegal, or age-restricted content report under the Australian Online Safety Act. We have received your submission and it is pending review. We will investigate this report in a timely manner. Please note this is only indicative, as it depends on many factors, including the complexity of the issues raised and how much relevant information you have included in your report. \nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nContent URL: {contentURL}\n\nFollowing our review of your complaint, we may decide that the content you reported violates Roblox’s Community Standards or requires us to take action under cited Australian laws (if so, we will take appropriate action) or we may decide that the content you reported does not violate Roblox’s Community Standards or require us to take action under cited Australian laws. \n\nYou will receive an update with our decision and details on any action taken to the contact email you provided.\nIf you would like to submit an additional report, please visit our reporting page: https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting.","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportLawEnforcement":"Thank you for submitting an Australian Online Safety Act Content Report. In order to be able to process this request efficiently, we kindly request that you submit it through our Law Enforcement Portal which can be found here: https://app.kodexglobal.com/roblox/signin. \nYou can find more information in our FAQs for law enforcement here: https://en.help.roblox.com/hc/en-us/articles/11219680442260-Help-Center-FAQs-for-Law-Enforcement.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportUserModerated":"Hello,\nThank you for submitting an Australian Online Safety Act Content report.\nAfter review of your submitted report, we have concluded that the behavior violates Roblox's Community Standards and the user has been moderated at the time of this response:\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\n\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportContentAlreadyRemoved":"Content Already Removed","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportContentRemoved":"Violation (OSA Reported Content Removed)","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportGeneralInquiries":"Report Irrelevant for ICR - General Inquiries","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportInsufficientInformation":"Insufficient Information for Illegal or Harmful Content Review","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportLawEnforcement":"Report From Law Enforcement","Description.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNewReport":"We are sorry, but we are unable to provide you with any further information or response regarding this inquiry. We encourage you to review the previous information sent to you, as we have provided you with all that we can at this time. If you would like to submit an additional report, please visit our reporting page: https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting.\nHowever, if you need further assistance with a different matter, please visit our Support Form: https://www.roblox.com/support.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nSincerely,\nThe Roblox Moderation Team","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportNewReport":"Please Submit a New Report","Heading.AuOSA.illegalContentReportUserModerated":"Violation (OSA Reported User Removed)","Action.Reply":"Reply","Description.AuOSANonCompliance.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Thank you for submitting a complaint under the Australian Online Safety Act.\nWe have received your request and it is now pending review.\nOur team will assess the information you provided and determine whether the matter raises any compliance issues under the Australian Online Safety Act or Roblox’s applicable obligations.\nPlease note that review timelines may vary depending on the complexity of the complaint and the level of detail included in your submission.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nOnce our review is complete, we will contact you at the email address you provided with our findings and any actions taken, if applicable.\nIf you would like to submit an additional complaint or report, please visit our reporting page:\n https://www.roblox.com/illegal-content-reporting","Heading.AuOSANonCompliance.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Illegal Content Report - Automated Reply to Newly Created Tickets","Heading.TrademarkPolicyViolation":"Trademark Policy Violation","Description.TrademarkPolicyViolation":"Hello,{linebreak}{linebreak}We delisted your asset (asset ID {ContentID}) because it may have contained a trademark owned by {Rightsholder} that you do not have permission to use. If you believe that this determination was in error, then you may appeal it here: {ModerationPortalURL}.{linebreak}{linebreak}Roblox respects the intellectual property rights of others and requires that all members of the Roblox community do the same, as stated in our {RobloxTermsOfUseURL} and {RobloxCommunityStandardsURL}. Creators are responsible for the assets they create, and group owners are responsible for the assets uploaded to their groups. Please review all of your content to ensure that you have the proper right or permission. If you would like to proactively archive any assets, then follow the steps outlined here: {RobloxAssetsURL}.{linebreak}{linebreak}Thank you,{linebreak}Roblox Support Team","Heading.GameContentScrubbed":"Game Content Scrubbed","Description.GameContentScrubbed":"Your game contains violative text flagged our text filter. Please rename your game appropriately.","Heading.USNCII.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"NCII Removal Request Received","Description.USNCII.illegalContentReportNewEmail":"Thank you for submitting a removal request for nonconsensual intimate imagery.\nWe have received your request and it is now pending review. Our team will assess the information you provided and take action on valid requests within 48 hours.\nTicket ID: {ticketID}\nIf you would like to submit an additional request, please visit: https://www.roblox.com/non-consensual-intimate-imagery-removal-request","ChatSummaries":"Chat summaries","Description.AutoGeneratedSummaries":"Roblox may auto-generate summaries of players’ messages.","AskParentToUnlockChat":"Ask a parent for permission to unlock chat with trusted friends."};
